1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 21]

2
00:00:22,856 --> 00:00:23,895
What are you doing here?

3
00:00:31,536 --> 00:00:32,095
What's wrong?

4
00:00:33,376 --> 00:00:34,295
Why so nervous?

5
00:00:34,776 --> 00:00:36,015
I'm still on duty.

6
00:00:36,256 --> 00:00:37,055
Why did you come?

7
00:00:42,416 --> 00:00:43,615
I came to see the doctor.

8
00:00:44,056 --> 00:00:45,375
What seems to be the problem?

9
00:00:50,736 --> 00:00:51,935
All day today,

10
00:00:52,456 --> 00:00:53,895
Every time I think of that person,

11
00:00:56,696 --> 00:00:58,055
my heart starts racing.

12
00:01:06,976 --> 00:01:08,695
Then I need to examine you thoroughly.

13
00:01:24,976 --> 00:01:26,255
It really is beating fast.

14
00:01:31,536 --> 00:01:32,895
Dr. Ye, is there

15
00:01:33,456 --> 00:01:34,375
hope for me?

16
00:01:37,616 --> 00:01:38,335
There is.

17
00:01:39,616 --> 00:01:41,175
Just stop thinking about that person.

18
00:01:48,976 --> 00:01:50,055
I'm afraid I can't do that.

19
00:01:51,896 --> 00:01:53,095
As a common person,

20
00:01:53,536 --> 00:01:55,095
my mind is filled with making money

21
00:01:55,336 --> 00:01:56,175
and that person.

22
00:02:00,256 --> 00:02:01,095
Enough.

23
00:02:01,536 --> 00:02:02,815
This is a hospital.

24
00:02:03,176 --> 00:02:03,895
Don't mess around.

25
00:02:15,336 --> 00:02:16,015
Hospital?

26
00:02:17,176 --> 00:02:19,055
Master He just invested this morning.

27
00:02:19,776 --> 00:02:21,135
Doesn't that make it my territory?

28
00:02:30,136 --> 00:02:32,175
I'm your last patient today.

29
00:02:33,016 --> 00:02:34,415
You must cure me

30
00:02:34,496 --> 00:02:35,575
before you leave.

31
00:02:43,056 --> 00:02:43,895
How do you want treatment?

32
00:02:52,336 --> 00:02:53,335
You're the doctor.

33
00:02:53,736 --> 00:02:54,455
You're asking me?

34
00:04:29,536 --> 00:04:32,215
Miss, buy some flowers! They're beautiful!

35
00:04:34,776 --> 00:04:35,535
Do you like flowers?

36
00:04:36,416 --> 00:04:37,295
Of course I do!

37
00:04:43,176 --> 00:04:44,415
I'll take this whole basket.

38
00:04:45,216 --> 00:04:46,295
Thank you, sir!

39
00:04:46,296 --> 00:04:47,335
You're so generous!

40
00:04:51,616 --> 00:04:52,215
For you.

41
00:04:53,456 --> 00:04:53,975
Thanks.

42
00:05:03,336 --> 00:05:04,215
Why did you take one stem

43
00:05:04,216 --> 00:05:05,175
out of the bunch?

44
00:05:07,856 --> 00:05:08,655
For observation.

45
00:05:09,216 --> 00:05:10,095
Observation?

46
00:05:10,776 --> 00:05:12,295
If this stem wilts,

47
00:05:12,776 --> 00:05:14,535
it means your bouquet has wilted too.

48
00:05:15,656 --> 00:05:17,295
Then I'll buy you new flowers.

49
00:05:17,656 --> 00:05:18,975
Don't you like flowers?

50
00:05:18,976 --> 00:05:20,295
I'll give you flowers for life.

51
00:05:22,856 --> 00:05:24,095
Is the head of the Zhou family

52
00:05:24,096 --> 00:05:26,295
promising me flowers for life?

53
00:05:27,096 --> 00:05:29,175
Are you seeking some commitment?

54
00:05:30,616 --> 00:05:31,215
What?

55
00:05:31,856 --> 00:05:33,095
You don't want to commit?

56
00:05:34,736 --> 00:05:36,535
Someone took advantage of me

57
00:05:37,616 --> 00:05:38,735
and won't take responsibility.

58
00:05:42,776 --> 00:05:43,775
But right now,

59
00:05:43,776 --> 00:05:45,215
I'm still an intern.

60
00:05:45,536 --> 00:05:46,735
My salary can't afford

61
00:05:46,736 --> 00:05:48,455
such a handsome man.

62
00:05:49,096 --> 00:05:49,855
So...

63
00:05:50,096 --> 00:05:51,295
I can't take responsibility.

64
00:05:54,536 --> 00:05:56,095
I promise I'm low maintenance.

65
00:05:56,856 --> 00:05:58,095
I won't cost you much.

66
00:06:34,216 --> 00:06:35,535
Lieutenant Yu!

67
00:06:35,776 --> 00:06:36,295
We were wrong!

68
00:06:36,296 --> 00:06:37,295
We know we were wrong!

69
00:06:37,296 --> 00:06:38,735
Lieutenant Yu!

70
00:06:40,336 --> 00:06:40,895
I know I was wrong!

71
00:06:40,896 --> 00:06:41,535
Spare our lives!

72
00:06:41,536 --> 00:06:42,535
I know I was wrong!

73
00:06:44,856 --> 00:06:46,415
You gathered to gamble and assault civilians.

74
00:06:46,416 --> 00:06:47,415
Punishable by military law.

75
00:06:51,536 --> 00:06:52,655
My apologies, Lieutenant Yu.

76
00:06:54,896 --> 00:06:55,735
[Zhongshan Hospital]

77
00:06:55,776 --> 00:06:56,295
Director Lin,

78
00:06:56,656 --> 00:06:57,655
why is this new doctor

79
00:06:57,656 --> 00:06:58,615
performing my surgery?

80
00:06:58,656 --> 00:06:59,735
She's so young.

81
00:06:59,896 --> 00:07:01,055
Does she have surgical experience?

82
00:07:01,296 --> 00:07:01,975
Director Lin,

83
00:07:02,336 --> 00:07:03,735
you must perform this surgery.

84
00:07:03,856 --> 00:07:06,095
Dr. Ye graduated from a medical school

85
00:07:06,456 --> 00:07:08,415
and has years of clinical experience.

86
00:07:08,536 --> 00:07:09,655
For minor injuries like yours,

87
00:07:09,856 --> 00:07:11,295
she's perfectly capable.

88
00:07:11,656 --> 00:07:12,655
Take it or leave it.

89
00:07:16,456 --> 00:07:17,615
Enough nonsense!

90
00:07:19,736 --> 00:07:20,655
I heard!

91
00:07:21,336 --> 00:07:22,775
Dr. Ye gets bullied at the hospital

92
00:07:23,056 --> 00:07:24,535
because of her lack of experience.

93
00:07:25,336 --> 00:07:25,975
So

94
00:07:26,456 --> 00:07:27,295
today

95
00:07:27,336 --> 00:07:28,775
I brought several wounded soldiers.

96
00:07:29,776 --> 00:07:31,295
They're already in the operating room.

97
00:07:34,856 --> 00:07:36,175
If you don't mind,

98
00:07:37,296 --> 00:07:37,895
I can send you

99
00:07:37,896 --> 00:07:39,215
a few wounded soldiers every day.

100
00:07:40,856 --> 00:07:42,095
If you refuse to operate,

101
00:07:42,096 --> 00:07:42,975
get out now!

102
00:07:43,416 --> 00:07:44,975
Go! Get moving!

103
00:07:47,616 --> 00:07:48,295
Director Lin,

104
00:07:48,856 --> 00:07:49,655
you should rest too.

105
00:07:51,296 --> 00:07:51,975
You...

106
00:07:52,656 --> 00:07:53,975
Can you handle this alone?

107
00:07:55,456 --> 00:07:56,615
I'll be fine, Director Lin.

108
00:07:57,096 --> 00:07:57,895
Lieutenant Yu,

109
00:07:58,616 --> 00:07:59,655
is my friend.

110
00:08:01,216 --> 00:08:01,975
What I meant is...

111
00:08:02,416 --> 00:08:03,335
with so many patients

112
00:08:03,856 --> 00:08:05,455
and insufficient anesthesia...

113
00:08:05,776 --> 00:08:07,055
Do whatever you want.

114
00:08:07,416 --> 00:08:08,455
Figure it out yourselves.

115
00:08:08,776 --> 00:08:10,735
But I want her to perform the surgery.

116
00:08:18,296 --> 00:08:19,095
Why are you glaring

117
00:08:19,096 --> 00:08:20,335
at your friend like that?

118
00:08:41,576 --> 00:08:42,295
Stop moving!

119
00:08:43,176 --> 00:08:44,055
If you move again,

120
00:08:44,056 --> 00:08:45,575
next time it won't be your leg.

121
00:08:50,176 --> 00:08:50,775
Dr. Ye,

122
00:08:51,176 --> 00:08:51,695
carry on.

123
00:09:31,736 --> 00:09:32,215
Here.

124
00:09:33,496 --> 00:09:34,695
Your favorite jasmine tea.

125
00:09:35,016 --> 00:09:35,695
To warm your hands.

126
00:09:36,296 --> 00:09:38,975
Did you cause their injuries?

127
00:09:40,296 --> 00:09:41,455
But they're all just

128
00:09:41,816 --> 00:09:43,135
unscrupulous gamblers

129
00:09:44,016 --> 00:09:45,255
with blood on their hands.

130
00:09:46,136 --> 00:09:46,855
Perfect timing.

131
00:09:47,216 --> 00:09:48,255
Giving you some performance metrics.

132
00:09:49,216 --> 00:09:50,175
I see.

133
00:09:59,576 --> 00:10:00,335
Rare occasion.

134
00:10:00,656 --> 00:10:01,255
Not scolding me.

135
00:10:01,656 --> 00:10:02,095
See?

136
00:10:02,536 --> 00:10:03,495
Being good is such a loss.

137
00:10:04,616 --> 00:10:06,015
Risked my life to protect you,

138
00:10:06,776 --> 00:10:07,695
only to be hated.

139
00:10:09,136 --> 00:10:09,815
Play the villain,

140
00:10:10,456 --> 00:10:11,575
and you understand me.

141
00:10:13,136 --> 00:10:14,175
Help me treat this wound.

142
00:10:23,416 --> 00:10:24,175
Looking at this?

143
00:10:27,856 --> 00:10:28,655
Forgotten already?

144
00:10:30,856 --> 00:10:32,255
You made this with your own hands.

145
00:10:34,256 --> 00:10:35,495
Let me disinfect it first.

146
00:10:38,696 --> 00:10:39,975
Since you joined the Marshal,

147
00:10:42,016 --> 00:10:42,895
you've changed quite a bit.

148
00:10:46,736 --> 00:10:47,895
Same to you.

149
00:10:49,656 --> 00:10:51,095
You aren't exactly a saint either.

150
00:10:52,696 --> 00:10:53,695
The entire Zhou family

151
00:10:54,096 --> 00:10:55,815
is under your thumb.

152
00:10:57,576 --> 00:10:58,335
Impressive.

153
00:11:02,336 --> 00:11:03,415
I've never claimed

154
00:11:03,416 --> 00:11:04,535
to be a good person.

155
00:11:04,736 --> 00:11:05,495
That's why

156
00:11:05,776 --> 00:11:06,855
we're perfect for each other.

157
00:11:08,576 --> 00:11:09,295
Same as usual.

158
00:11:10,176 --> 00:11:11,295
Exit and turn right to pay.

159
00:11:11,816 --> 00:11:12,495
Thanks.

160
00:11:22,176 --> 00:11:22,775
Master.

161
00:11:23,176 --> 00:11:24,655
Since we switched from oil-paper

162
00:11:24,656 --> 00:11:25,775
to sealed porcelain jars,

163
00:11:26,056 --> 00:11:26,975
Our tea sales-

164
00:11:26,976 --> 00:11:28,215
have significantly improved.

165
00:11:28,856 --> 00:11:29,695
This month's profit margin

166
00:11:29,696 --> 00:11:30,615
rose nearly 20%.

167
00:11:30,896 --> 00:11:31,855
These days,

168
00:11:31,856 --> 00:11:33,055
the tea mountain elders

169
00:11:33,056 --> 00:11:34,255
are all smiling.

170
00:11:35,816 --> 00:11:36,575
Well done.

171
00:11:37,656 --> 00:11:38,535
I didn't expect you

172
00:11:38,536 --> 00:11:39,695
to be so full of ideas.

173
00:11:41,216 --> 00:11:42,095
Thank you, Master,

174
00:11:42,536 --> 00:11:43,455
for giving me

175
00:11:43,456 --> 00:11:44,935
the chance to prove myself.

176
00:11:45,896 --> 00:11:46,775
No need.

177
00:11:47,856 --> 00:11:48,775
Thank yourself.

178
00:11:50,016 --> 00:11:50,895
You pretended to be a ghost

179
00:11:51,096 --> 00:11:52,415
to unsettle the Zhou household,

180
00:11:52,856 --> 00:11:54,895
and helped me gather information inside.

181
00:11:55,136 --> 00:11:56,015
Your contributions are invaluable.

182
00:11:57,616 --> 00:11:58,255
I know,

183
00:11:58,896 --> 00:12:00,375
you have ambition and aspirations.

184
00:12:01,376 --> 00:12:02,535
Now that I hold power,

185
00:12:03,656 --> 00:12:04,175
you

186
00:12:05,016 --> 00:12:05,775
and Jinbao

187
00:12:07,896 --> 00:12:09,655
will receive your rightful rewards.

188
00:12:17,136 --> 00:12:18,295
Master, you seem

189
00:12:18,616 --> 00:12:19,935
in particularly good spirits today.

190
00:12:20,376 --> 00:12:20,975
Oh?

191
00:12:22,136 --> 00:12:22,775
Yes..

192
00:12:23,176 --> 00:12:25,135
Ever since returning from dinner with Ms. Ye,

193
00:12:25,176 --> 00:12:26,615
you haven't stopped smiling.

194
00:12:28,496 --> 00:12:29,775
Is it that obvious?

195
00:12:33,736 --> 00:12:34,455
Master,

196
00:12:34,736 --> 00:12:35,535
by the way,

197
00:12:35,856 --> 00:12:37,015
what does Ms. Ye do

198
00:12:37,096 --> 00:12:38,295
to make a living now?

199
00:12:39,216 --> 00:12:40,575
She seems quite mysterious.

200
00:12:40,976 --> 00:12:42,335
Could you share a hint?

201
00:12:44,376 --> 00:12:45,255
I'm afraid not.

202
00:12:46,136 --> 00:12:47,455
She wishes

203
00:12:47,456 --> 00:12:49,295
to achieve something noteworthy first.

204
00:12:52,096 --> 00:12:52,695
For now,

205
00:12:52,896 --> 00:12:53,575
it's confidential.

206
00:12:55,736 --> 00:12:56,975
I hadn't realized Ms. Ye

207
00:12:57,136 --> 00:12:58,295
was so career-driven.

208
00:12:58,856 --> 00:13:00,175
You're truly fortunate.

209
00:13:00,776 --> 00:13:01,575
Nanxi,

210
00:13:03,016 --> 00:13:04,415
you're being rather talkative today.

211
00:13:08,096 --> 00:13:09,255
But since I'm in good spirits,

212
00:13:10,016 --> 00:13:11,215
I'll let it slide.

213
00:13:11,736 --> 00:13:12,455
I'm leaving.

214
00:13:14,856 --> 00:13:20,735
♪ I have fallen into this Plum Blossom Temple... ♪

215
00:13:20,736 --> 00:13:22,455
Do you hear something?

216
00:13:23,376 --> 00:13:24,455
Opera singing.

217
00:13:25,016 --> 00:13:31,695
♪ My life has been filled with much affection... ♪

218
00:13:37,696 --> 00:13:42,575
♪ I have fallen into this... ♪

219
00:13:47,496 --> 00:13:49,135
Send her back to her hometown later.

220
00:13:49,216 --> 00:13:50,255
Give her ample silver.

221
00:13:53,016 --> 00:13:54,015
My father's dead.

222
00:13:54,616 --> 00:13:56,375
Her punishment should end.

223
00:13:57,576 --> 00:13:58,615
Are you certain?

224
00:13:58,976 --> 00:14:00,855
She once harmed you and Ms. Ye.

225
00:14:01,496 --> 00:14:02,535
From now on,

226
00:14:03,696 --> 00:14:05,375
she can never harm us again.

227
00:14:06,416 --> 00:14:08,495
I'm going to marry Ye Zhiqiu honorably.

228
00:14:32,896 --> 00:14:33,735
Third Concubine.

229
00:14:34,976 --> 00:14:35,975
You came?

230
00:14:37,576 --> 00:14:38,415
Third Concubine.

231
00:14:38,936 --> 00:14:40,015
What do you mean?

232
00:14:40,696 --> 00:14:41,655
After the Qing Dynasty fell,

233
00:14:41,656 --> 00:14:42,655
Manchu people declined.

234
00:14:42,936 --> 00:14:43,695
My brother owed gambling debts,

235
00:14:43,696 --> 00:14:44,895
and wanted to sell me to a brothel.

236
00:14:45,536 --> 00:14:46,855
You took pity on me

237
00:14:47,576 --> 00:14:48,735
and bought me back.

238
00:14:49,656 --> 00:14:50,455
I will remember

239
00:14:51,536 --> 00:14:52,935
your kindness forever.

240
00:14:55,816 --> 00:14:57,375
I thought after you climbed the social ladder,

241
00:14:57,736 --> 00:14:59,935
you wouldn't care about your outdated master anymore.

242
00:15:01,016 --> 00:15:02,695
But you still have a conscience.

243
00:15:07,576 --> 00:15:09,455
Master agreed to let you retire to your hometown.

244
00:15:09,736 --> 00:15:11,295
He also allocated a generous sum for you.

245
00:15:12,776 --> 00:15:14,895
Zhou Yimo would show such sincerity?

246
00:15:17,736 --> 00:15:19,615
He agreed to let me retire at home?

247
00:15:20,936 --> 00:15:22,495
He is open and honorable.

248
00:15:23,096 --> 00:15:24,135
If he says he'll release you,

249
00:15:24,336 --> 00:15:25,255
he means it.

250
00:15:25,816 --> 00:15:26,935
You can rest assured.

251
00:15:34,456 --> 00:15:35,135
Nanxi,

252
00:15:35,776 --> 00:15:36,495
thank you.

253
00:15:41,336 --> 00:15:42,135
Third Concubine.

254
00:15:44,016 --> 00:15:45,255
You're finally free.

255
00:15:49,096 --> 00:15:49,855
Farewell.

256
00:16:22,496 --> 00:16:23,655
Why are you here?
